import React from "react"; function Disclaimer() { return (

Disclaimers:

  • Investment Risk:

    • All investments carry risks, including unlisted stocks. Be aware of potential losses.

  • Data Accuracy:

    • While we strive for accurate data, information may change. Verify details independently

  • Educational Purpose:

    • Our predictions are tools for informed decisions, not guaranteed outcomes.

  • Consult a Professional:

    • Always consult a financial advisor or do your own research before making investment decisions.

  • Privacy:

    • We value your privacy and adhere to strict data protection standards.

  • Terms and Conditions:

    • Read our Terms of Use and Privacy Policy for a detailed understanding of our platform's rules.

  • Contact Us:

    • For inquiries or concerns, feel free to reach out to our support team.
); } export default Disclaimer;
